{"tid":1353201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復元朗，要更理性，更和理非。","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:53:00.000Z","uid":175673,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac00d271d6eca95b7e3927e44adfdadbe186115d","tid":1353201,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:19:05.000Z","msg":"光復元朗，不但要比之前更多人，仲要更理性，更和理非。<br />\n要表達 政警黑 3體連成一體。<br />\n增加西方國家比中國更大壓力。<br />\n硬撞硬，火遮眼，正中下懷。<br />\n堅持劍指政權。<br />\n除左黑警，一定要帶出鄉黑都係政權一部分，依一點一定要比西方國家知。<br />\n<br />\n我地勢力只有和理非，勇武，真記者，文宣。<br />\n一直我地做到既事就係make noise。引起外國關注。<br />\n<br />\n中共勢力有政，警，鄉黑，5毛，tvb等紅媒。<br />\n中共怕既係政權穩定，最怕亂，怕亂局感染到國內城市。<br />\n<br />\n最後，真香港人而家就係豪賭，中共覺得政權穩定重要，定係香港依個生金蛋既雞重要。換句話，會唔會為左滅聲，平亂而派解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n另一結局，就係7婆答應晒5大訴求，平息事件。"},{"pid":"95a82f44b8e5be232bf18a1e1074446b04d7184d","tid":1353201,"uid":280305,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"光復元朗？係元朗人做，唔係其他地區人去做！"},{"pid":"d3547d85077705d9a420028c97e6dc12c9eb1447","tid":1353201,"uid":175673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95a82f44b8e5be232bf18a1e1074446b04d7184d","tid":1353201,"uid":280305,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"光復元朗？係元朗人做，唔係其他地區人去做！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:22:28.000Z","msg":"名叫光復元朗，實係光復香港。劍指政警鄉黑。<br />\n住得元朗，就最怕被點相，唔駛諗住會多元朗人會出黎。"},{"pid":"3a22dfa3f552f49f948eaff1476a9c5ab4ed8226","tid":1353201,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257be579300ef9d5842e4cccf867b5a7ea8abb87","tid":1353201,"uid":280305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:23:30.000Z","msg":"我係想話，目標明確，要對付黑社會，冇問題！<br />\n但要有具體實質目的，入去鳩行鳩叫，不如行街睇戲！"},{"pid":"8d1a78fbe8bb4c6498943892b8cae5d6a23cb9a5","tid":1353201,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:28:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"af4d6d9a4c81d18be93d2ba655996d8ac224b9a4","tid":1353201,"uid":215265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"其實元朗有好多中產，今次鄉黑搞埋佢地，我地出嚟佢地都會支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353031</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"3ae9b00a3811183e5f9ff51c74ecde20375dcdad","tid":1353201,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257be579300ef9d5842e4cccf867b5a7ea8abb87","tid":1353201,"uid":280305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:23:30.000Z","msg":"我係想話，目標明確，要對付黑社會，冇問題！<br />\n但要有具體實質目的，入去鳩行鳩叫，不如行街睇戲！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:16.000Z","msg":"警黑合作，我地由始至終都唔會打得入。<br />\n而家做到既係要夠多noise。<br />\n要比外界知而家香港比中共攪到有幾咁亂，幾咁差。<br />\n難得對家助攻，要珍惜機會。"},{"pid":"9c143a8bc0a92763b1d3dd9840d0364c94737b33","tid":1353201,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"南邊圍，算唔算清晰目標？"},{"pid":"cf3be2bc628dbee8e8ac2644f3e7dc158c9414ab","tid":1353201,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c143a8bc0a92763b1d3dd9840d0364c94737b33","tid":1353201,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"南邊圍，算唔算清晰目標？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"要人多到佢地村都唔敢行出半步就夠。"},{"pid":"f37058e94b1b32472e2204fe5ab8a715969da920","tid":1353201,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c143a8bc0a92763b1d3dd9840d0364c94737b33","tid":1353201,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"南邊圍，算唔算清晰目標？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"南邊圍討伐"},{"pid":"e527312542c5ff228b3d6958a61f24889d650631","tid":1353201,"uid":279925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a82f44b8e5be232bf18a1e1074446b04d7184d","tid":1353201,"uid":280305,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedB