y":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c8a2c633e658402e57651135ea699733724500","tid":1353201,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"192ec3aa0fbba9a58d39edaa94adb06f4cfd0caa","tid":1353201,"uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"有gear 保護到自己一定最重要，引到佢攻先我地就贏左noise。<br />\n同樣，武都唔係唔好。但要去到咩程度?<br />\n我地可以武到先打低黑警，再燒村屠村嗎？<br />\n<br />\n就算武，都要有目的。"},{"pid":"7bd6fd0227001116eb7a8dfb2cf3620ae7b0bc92","tid":1353201,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:53:00.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}